# Real YT Music Library Sync + AI Smart Playlist

## Goal

Upgrade the music feature so the AI agent **actually goes into the user's YT Music account** (using the cookie already provided), fetches their real data (liked songs, recently played, listen again), analyzes their taste with AI, and creates a smart playlist they can play in-app.

## Flow

```
User connects YT Music (cookie) → Agent fetches real library data
→ AI analyzes patterns (genres, artists, moods, languages)
→ AI generates a personalized "Smart Playlist" with new song recommendations
→ Songs display in a playlist view → user plays them in-app
```

